title: Wolverine & Power Pack 01-04 (2009|GreenGiant-DCP)
description:
This All-Ages tale is by Marc Sumerak and features some fun interactions with the mostly humorless Wolverine and the bouncy brats from Power Pack. Promotional info - "The Power kids are excited to be visiting the coolest school on the planet - the Xavier Institute! But even the home of the world's most powerful mutants might not be safe when the Sentinels come knocking! It's mutant mayhem in the mighty Marvel manner!

All four issues are by GreenGiant-DCP. This fills a request from KAT. Please seed, and enjoy! :-)
